95	## Testes de Erro
96	
97	Tão importantes quanto os de sucesso:
98	
99	```php
100	public function test_transfer_fails_with_insufficient_funds(): void {
101	    $repo = new InMemoryAccountRepository();
102	    $repo->save(new Account('A', 100));
103	    $repo->save(new Account('B', 0));
104	    $service = new AccountService($repo);
105	
106	    $this->expectException(InsufficientFundsException::class);
107	    $service->transfer('A', 'B', 500);
108	
109	    // Verifica que saldo NÃO mudou
110	    $this->assertEquals(100, $repo->findById('A')->balance);
111	}
112	
113	public function test_transfer_fails_with_nonexistent_account(): void {
114	    $this->expectException(AccountNotFoundException::class);
115	    $service->transfer('INEXISTENTE', 'B', 100);
116	}
117	```
