119	## PEST (alternativa moderna)
120	
121	```php
122	it('transfers money between accounts', function () {
123	    $repo = new InMemoryAccountRepository();
124	    $repo->save(new Account('A', 1000));
125	    $repo->save(new Account('B', 500));
126	    $service = new AccountService($repo);
127	
128	    $service->transfer('A', 'B', 300);
129	
130	    expect($repo->findById('A')->balance)->toBe(700)
131	        ->and($repo->findById('B')->balance)->toBe(800);
132	});
133	
134	it('rejects transfer with insufficient funds')
135	    ->throws(InsufficientFundsException::class);
136	```
